snippet.title: Flyhunter Origins Trailer
snippet.description:
Take on the role of Zak; a bumbling alien spaceship janitor and wannabe Flyhunter!

Zak works on board the Flyhunter Crew’s legendary spaceship; ‘The Frog’, but deep down he longs for an exciting adventure of his own…

Somewhere in Earth’s orbit, while the Flyhunters are deep in cryo sleep; The Frog’s important cargo of extremely rare insects is mysteriously jettisoned into space, crash-landing back on Earth. It seems that the clumsy janitor Zak is the only one around to save the day. Can this accidental hero swap his sweeping brush for a super-cool fly swatter and take on the role of daring Flyhunter? 

As featured in Tegrazone 

Find out more at: http://www.flyhunter.com/
